### Create portfolio
POST http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "initialCash": 10000.00
}

### Deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{ "amount": 2500.00 }

### Buy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "quantity": 5.0,
  "price": 180.25
}

### Sell
POST http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio/sell
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "quantity": 2.0,
  "price": 190.00
}

### Valuation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio/valuation
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

